	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quoties ad d. <persName type="auto_name">Guarnerum</persName> et nostrum d. <persName type="auto_name">Lelium</persName> dedi literas, totus ab illis petii, ut te accederent, meis verbis reverenter salutarent ac de omnibus certiorem redderent, quod eos fecisse non dubito.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc etiam ex meis ad.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">d. <persName type="auto_name">Guarnerum</persName> et quibusdam scriptis intelliges, quo in statu sint nostrę, multaque narrabit et d. <persName type="citizen_name">Iulius Maresius</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1709">Bellunensis</placeName>, vir eruditus, quem dominus per me eruit ex <placeName type="citizen_name"><persName type="citizen_name">Francisci</persName></placeName> antro.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Venit istuc eo animo, ut vestra pia pariter et erudita fruatur consuetudine.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Optat convictor esse d. <persName ref="p2336" cert="high">Bernardini</persName> aut d. <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicani</persName>; ut illum suscipiet, accipiet a me singulis annis, quantum iusserit.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogo, ut tu quoque hominem novitium in christiana palestra solita tua charitate complectaris.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Erat in papatu doctor theologię ex nobili familia.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc scribo, ut nihil ignores.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quam gratę fuerint ecclesię <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonicę</placeName> tuę litere, cognosces ex responsis, que tibi mitto.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus te diutissime ecclesię suę servet.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta ex me optimam tuam coniugem, filios, filias, generos et, si tamen audere licet, clarissimos viros d. consules, archigrammateum et thesaurarios.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum ex <placeName type="citizen_name">Heremo Sarmatic</placeName> 14. augusti 1556.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1936" cert="high">Franciscus Lismaninus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Doctrina et eruditione pręstantissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henricho Bulingero</persName>, ecclesiae Tiguri[nae] pastori vigilantissimo, domino [et] fratri colendissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
